      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead-big"><strong>Use of face coverings on campus</strong></span></p>
<p>While you are not required to wear a face covering on campus, we would support those who choose to do so. See the <a href="https://www.gov.scot/publications/coronavirus-covid-19-staying-safe-and-protecting-others/">Scottish Government website</a> for more advice on when to wear a face covering. </p>
<p style="font-weight: 400;"><span class="lead-big"><strong>Protecting yourself and others from COVID</strong></span></p>
<p>Although all COVID rules and restrictions have been lifted in Scotland, the virus has not gone away. </p>
<p>Please use 'COVID sense' to help protect yourself and others, and to reduce pressure on health services. This means that you should:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.nhsinform.scot/covid-19-vaccine/"><strong>Get your vaccine </strong></a>when offered to ensure you are fully protected.</li>
<li><a href="https://www.nhsinform.scot/illnesses-and-conditions/infections-and-poisoning/coronavirus-covid-19/coronavirus-covid-19"><strong>Stay at home </strong></a><strong>if you’re unwell</strong> with symptoms or have a fever (see our <a href="/coronavirus/faqs/accommodation/"><strong>Accommodation coronavirus FAQs</strong></a> for advice if you live on campus).</li>
<li><strong>Open windows</strong> when socialising indoors.</li>
<li><a href="https://www.gov.scot/publications/coronavirus-covid-19-staying-safe-and-protecting-others/pages/face-coverings/">Where appropriate, wear a face covering </a>in indoor public places and on public transport. (<strong>While you are not required to wear a face covering on campus, we would support those who choose to do so.)</strong></li>
<li><strong>Keep your hands clean </strong>by washing them regularly throughout the day and using the hand gel at sanitiser stations on campus.</li>
</ul>
<p>For <a href="https://www.nhsinform.scot/illnesses-and-conditions/infections-and-poisoning/coronavirus-covid-19/coronavirus-covid-19-general-advice"><strong>advice on symptoms and what to do if you think you have coronavirus, visit NHS Inform</strong></a>.</p>
<p>For more information on how QMU is responding to COVID, including <a href="/coronavirus/faqs/">FAQs</a>, see our coronavirus <a href="/coronavirus/">website</a>.</p>
<div class="mceNonEditable embeditem" data-embed-url="https://youtu.be/oLxB_jC-OkI" data-embed-height="346" data-embed-width="720" data-embed-constrain="true"><iframe width="615" height="346" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oLxB_jC-OkI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" title="COVID sense at QMU"></iframe></div>
<p><span class="lead-big">Hygiene</span></p>
<p>On campus, we have an extensive set of safety measures in place, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>hand sanitizing stations (including hand sanitizers plus wipes etc as appropriate).</li>
<li>enhanced hygiene procedures;</li>
<li>good ventilation;</li>
<li>signage in place to advise on health and safety and to ensure the safe flow of students and staff through our buildings.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="lead lead-big">COVID-friendly catering</span></p>
<p>With a number of catering outlets across the campus, we can provide our high quality catering while avoiding congestion and offer an online ordering and collection app. Find out more about <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/7ac62a9a0ac442c78ae93816a9e60377}" title="Eat and Shop on Campus">eating and shopping on campus</a>. </p>
<p><span class="lead lead-big">Space for private study</span></p>
<p>As our Learning Resource Centre forms a full quarter of our main academic building, we are well placed to provide study space that allows you to avoid being closer than you might like to be to others. Find out more on our <a href="/{localLink:umb://document/71b99825061d4a2e8bd48daeb9d7cfe2}" title="Library" data-udi="umb://document/120cabb51c9d4e569ef5b977b9a4451d">Library</a> website.</p>
<p><span class="lead lead-big">Fresh air and green space</span></p>
<p>There is plenty of inspiring outdoor space to enjoy in and around our beautiful campus grounds.</p>
<p style="font-weight: 400;"> </p>]]></Value>
